{"type":"message","id":"947b8aa9","parentId":"c7de487a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T23:24:41.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now compare the current state against the baseline state from heartbeat-state.json (saved at 23:11 UTC).\n\n**Baseline (23:11 UTC):**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d`: running ✅\n- `cron:e7885813`: done (ended ~22:42 UTC)\n- `cron:6f3323ef`: running (normal cycle restart)\n- `main`: done\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134`: done\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258`: done\n- `telegramDeliveryIssue`: active since 22:47 UTC\n\n\n- `cron:53c5832a`: running (Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7) — NEW, not in baseline\n- `cron:e7885813-0446-4101`: running (Agent Status to Lead) — NEW instance, not in baseline\n- `cron:e7885813`: still running in current state (23:23 UTC) — appears to be a new instance that wasn't in the baseline\n- `cron:6f3323ef`: also running but not listed in the baseline snapshot\n\nLooking at the main session, it shows as done in the baseline but appears to be running in the current state, though that might just be stale data from an earlier check. The 5p QLHV monitor is still running with its three child sessions completing normally. Comparing the current time of 23:24 UTC against the baseline at 23:11 UTC, I'm seeing two new cron jobs that weren't in the baseline: the daily briefing at 5AM UTC+7 and the agent status report to lead, both spawned after the baseline snapshot. Looking at the session timeline, I can see the baseline ended around 23:11 UTC, and there's a new agent status check running from 23:14-23:15 UTC, plus the daily briefing at 23:16 UTC. So compared to the 23:11 baseline, the pipeline remains healthy with the new sessions appearing as expected lifecycle events rather than failures.\n\nSince the cron:e7885813 session is still active and these are just normal agent status checks wrapping up, there's nothing new to report to the group. I'll stay quiet and update the heartbeat state instead.","thinkingSignature":"b566e9f1c092ff1e8f9794d6c99da3cc08ab35cc0d90704207f96e17f28bcbdd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9l6gaysjjna1_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"lastChecked\": \"2026-04-14T23:24:00Z\",\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"cron:ed2d0b5d\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"5p QLHV monitor\", \"note\": \"running ~5h45m, 3 child sessions completed\" },\n    \"cron:e7885813\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Agent Status to Lead\", \"note\": \"new instance 23:14 UTC\" },\n    \"cron:6f3323ef\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"DTLX 5p Monitor\", \"note\": \"normal 5-min cycle restart\" },\n    \"cron:53c5832a\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7\", \"note\": \"NEW instance 23:16 UTC\" },\n    \"main\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"note\": \"expected\" },\n    \"telegram:direct:6053576134\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"note\": \"ended ~22:02 UTC\" },\n    \"telegram:group:-5163901258\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"note\": \"ended ~21:49 UTC — was stale\" }\n  },\n  \"telegramDeliveryIssue\": {\n    \"since\": \"2026-04-14T22:47:00Z\",\n    \"symptom\": \"sessions_send to telegram:group:-5163901258 times out\",\n    \"note\": \"May need gateway restart or Telegram bot re-auth\"\n  },\n  \"pipeline\": \"HEALTHY\",\n  \"blockers\": []\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":21844,"output":887,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":422,"totalTokens":37097,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776209063655,"responseId":"062dffa805c3d68b55ebf2b1b4b69b31"}}
